            "description": "Get all orders with comprehensive filtering:\n\n**Pagination:**\n- page: Page number\n- limit: Items per page\n\n**Status Filter:**\n- all, pending, confirmed, shipped, delivered, cancelled\n\n**Sort Options:**\n- pending_first: Pending orders first (default)\n- newest: Most recent first\n- oldest: Oldest first\n- amount_high: Highest amount first\n- amount_low: Lowest amount first\n\n**Date Filters:**\n- all: All orders\n- today: Today's orders\n- yesterday: Yesterday's orders\n- this_week: This week's orders\n- this_month: This month's orders\n- last_month: Last month's orders\n- custom: Custom date range (requires startDate & endDate)\n\n**Additional Filters:**\n- search: Search order ID, user email, or name\n- paymentMethod: Filter by payment method\n- paymentStatus: Filter by payment status\n- deliveryStatus: Filter by delivery status"
